# Grimverse Asset Audit Rule

Before a shot is promoted:
- verify the referenced image_source exists
- verify the referenced video_source exists
- verify the source paths are vault-relative and not placeholder text
- verify the run/review chain is complete for the same shot id
- verify the shot status is one of the approved production states

## Failure behavior
- Stop on missing assets
- Stop on broken asset paths
- Stop on unresolved placeholder references
- Do not mark a shot complete unless the file exists
